          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Safe Home Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Child Abuse Prevention and Treatment Act to make unregulated custody transfers of children to strangers a form of child abuse and neglect, therefore allowing child-welfare agencies to investigate such transfers.</p>]]></text>
